blocks.en:
flowchart TD
  A[Frame arrives] --> B{Mode?}
  B -->|Mode 0| C{SEC bit set?}
  C -->|Yes| D[Discard: UNAVAILABLE-KEY]
  C -->|No| E[Process normally]
  B -->|Mode 1| F{SEC value expected?}
  F -->|No| G[Error: INVALID-SEC-VALUE]
  F -->|Yes| H[Decrypt + integrity + freshness checks]

blocks.zh:
flowchart TD
  A[帧到达] --> B{模式?}
  B -->|模式 0| C{SEC 位置一?}
  C -->|是| D[丢弃: UNAVAILABLE-KEY]
  C -->|否| E[正常处理]
  B -->|模式 1| F{SEC 值符合预期?}
  F -->|否| G[错误: INVALID-SEC-VALUE]
  F -->|是| H[解密 + 完整性 + 新鲜性校验]
